title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Wickerwork & Basketwork
description: Imports of Intra EU - Wickerwork & Basketwork in the United Kingdom decreased to 0.74 GBP Million in September from 0.91 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Wickerwork & Basketwork in the United Kingdom averaged 0.58 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 14.27 GBP Million in March of 2022 and a record low of 0.09 GBP Million in December of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Wickerwork & Basketwork.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
